      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUPER SEQUIOA (6) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 0.8 lengths at Q Straight in a handy 16.82 beating Do Run Bandi. One of the key runners again. FARMOR ENVY (4) showed good early burn and was there until turning but swamped late to finish 7th at this track in a Mix 5. Should be about the money. SHE'S ATHLETIC (1) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 5th (20.08) at this track. Goes very well from this draw with four wins and two minor placings from 10 starts. Deserves plenty of respect. KEEP YOU POSTED (8) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to make amends.",
